  <name>Budgie Control Center</name>
  <summary>Utility to configure desktop settings</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Budgie Control Center is the primary interface for configuring your system. It is a fork of GNOME Settings / GNOME Control Center with the intent of providing a simplified list of settings that are applicable to the Budgie 10 series, along with any small quality-of-life settings.
    </p>
